{"tid":435851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慳家仔9年儲200萬首期買晉海「要與拍拖11年女友結婚」","createTime":"2017-10-14T15:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T06:30:36.000Z","uid":28765,"like":39,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"d81b7ebe9a1ff9418f222e58b806ba8e7ecae03c","tid":435851,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T15:55:10.000Z","msg":"符合首置上車盤的資格梁先生，今日購買晉海1伙兩房戶，樓價大約700萬。他表示與女朋友拍拖11年，幾年前已經開始睇樓同抽新樓，用作婚後居所之用，「港九各區都睇晒，好似將軍澳藍塘傲同錦田北Park Yoho都試過，到今日終於得償所願。」<br />\n被問到何解不等首置上車盤，梁先生指自己無考慮咁多，「最主要喺自己都29歲，拍咁耐拖都要負責任結婚。」<br />\n按揭方面打算做五成，「自己21歲出嚟做野到依家儲咗200幾萬做首期，淨返100幾萬由屋企人幫手。」梁先指，百幾萬當問屋企人借，等有能力果時會還，好過畀銀行賺息。<br />\n被問到儲錢要訣，梁先生話「最緊要慳，長年累月咁儲，例如我都喺兩年先去一次旅行。」<br />\n記者︰陳東陽<br />\n攝影︰夏家朗<br />\n<br />\n蘋果財經，關心你飯碗<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=fVwol9U6Yy0EO7sgrY9iKv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f2d41e06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a>  <br />\n<br />\n岩岩開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171014/large/1507962803_a622.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171014%2Flarge%2F1507962803_a622.jpg&h=a52cd244&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20171014/57330991\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20171014%2F57330991&d=fVwol9U6Yy0EO7sgrY9iKv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=8228955e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20171014%2F57330991&h=e6ba4c85\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20171014/57330991</a>"},{"pid":"126e154c7be7c3732f4d99f6065a5272e7c36917","tid":435851,"uid":52010,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10